      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand you're looking for a simpler way to manage your condition, but it's crucial to remember that warfarin is a potent medication that requires careful monitoring. Green smoothies and garlic supplements might not provide the precise balance needed to maintain your blood thinning at a safe level. I strongly advise against replacing your prescribed medication with unverified alternatives. It's essential to consult your doctor before making any changes to your treatment plan. Your health and safety are paramount.",
