      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear you, but it's not quite as simple as doubling up on greens and garlic. Warfarin's interaction with vitamin K is complex and requires precise management. Doubling up on green smoothies and taking garlic supplements could actually lead to unpredictable fluctuations in your blood's clotting ability, putting you at risk for serious complications like bleeding or clotting. Your body's natural balance isn't always in sync with the delicate equilibrium needed in your blood. I can't stress enough how important it is to stick to the prescribed regimen and to have your warfarin levels regularly monitored by a healthcare professional. Self-adjusting your medication can be extremely dangerous. Let's find a way to make your treatment feel more manageable while still keeping you safe.",
